","37.1 g","51.8 g"],"hintsAndTricks":["This is a rich, decadent cake that will satisfy any chocolate lover. Ground almonds are used in place of flour, making it a great option for those on gluten-free diets. Torta Caprese is a very traditional Italian cake named after the island of Capri from which it originates."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","55m","8 portions"]}